1.Name: Observer Effect
1.Desc:
<color=#FFFFFF>Additional Ability</color>
When there's at least 2 <color=#FFFFFF>Krampus Compliance Authority</color> characters in your squad: When an Agent uses an <color=#FFFFFF>EX Special Attack</color>, Birkblick's Daze inflicted increases by 4%, stacking up to 3 times and lasting 15s. Repeated triggers reset the duration. At 3 stacks, DMG increases by 10%.
